rgy needs are taken into close consideration as vegetarian wheat and dairy-free options are available.The Caneles de Bordeaux is an other product of Ohlala.A Caneles is a cake with a rich custardy interior enclosed by a thin caramelized shell and are home made family recipe. I use a specific mould to cook them.They are very tasty and unique .~Have you had a stall at Yalukit Willam Ngargee or St Kilda Festival before?~No~', 0),
